channel.title: How do I
channel.description: I want to remove the table at the camelot party room. And yes I've already tried: [code]deletethatobject(2735, 3468);[/code] The camelot party room coords are 2735, 3467. I need help here :S.

deletethatobject(2735, 3468);

The camelot party room coords are 2735, 3467. I need help here :S.

maybe you dint remove it correcly just saying
remove in from the most bottom west cords.

[u][b]Juse because he changes the coords that he’s deleting, won’t mean the table will just vanish.

To fully remove the table, you MUST delete ALL coordinates that the table overlies.[/b][/u]
[/quote]

not really i remove bottom left from my server and it worked.[/quote]

ps: to the one in the blue: you are correct

answered for the retart with the bolded, underlined, red quote.

explanation
it only matters on where the object is being set.

example
beds they are not a 4 full blocked squared object they rest on one block then it fills in the other 3 so since he really doesnt know what he is doing is is safer for him to remove it from all the cords it is reseting at.
